Package kaitech.api.database

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IngredientTable
    The IngredientTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify ingredients in the database.
    InventoryTable
    The InventoryTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify ingredients and their quantity in the database.
    LoyaltyCardSettingsTable  
    LoyaltyCardTable
    The LoyaltyCardTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify loyalty cards in the database.
    MenuItemTable
    The MenuItemTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify MenuItems in the database.
    MenuTable
    The MenuTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify menus in the database.
    PinTable
    The PinTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify PINs in the database.
    RecipeTable
    The RecipeTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify recipes in the database.
    SaleTable
    The SaleTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify sales in the database.
    SupplierTable
    The SupplierTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify suppliers in the database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTable
    The AbstractTable class is, as it is named, an abstract class providing utility methods to the database table implementation classes.
